{"tid":1189749,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球港人拍照抗惡法","createTime":"2019-06-07T02:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T16:14:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9de51ba4a8688940318969984555b3e23b6f615","tid":1189749,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190607/20697909\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190607%2F20697909&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e6DV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=6e2239e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190607%2F20697909&h=79c2b5fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190607/20697909</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球港人拍照抗惡法<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190607/large/07la4p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190607%2Flarge%2F07la4p2.jpg&h=c800ee4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玻利維亞「天空之鏡」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府硬推《逃犯條例》修訂，勢將打破中港法治區隔的防火牆，遭到各界強烈反對，民陣將於6月9日舉行反惡法大遊行。早前有人發起海外港人「守護香港反送中網上行動」，呼籲手持反送中標語或海報拍照並上載至社交平台，以響應全球反送中大遊行集會。不少身在海外的港人紛紛表態聲援，並於6月9日在多個國家舉辦集會以示支持。<br />\n<br />\n該行動強調，身在海外的港人縱使未能出席6月9日大遊行，仍可在網上撐香港，盡綿力表達聲音互相支持，呼籲海外港人可自製標語或在facebook搜尋「#香港設計師反對逃犯條例修訂」的設計海報 ，列印後拿着在當地地標拍照，並將相片上載至facebook、Instagram及Twitter。連日來已經有不少身在英、美等國家的港人在當地舉起標語拍照上載，包括英國倫敦、英國牛津大學、美國康奈爾大學等。公民黨立法會議員楊岳橋亦在fb轉載多個海外港人拍照反送中的帖文。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190607/large/07la4p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190607%2Flarge%2F07la4p3.jpg&h=04aaeed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國<br />\n牛津<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190607/large/07la4p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190607%2Flarge%2F07la4p4.jpg&h=0e6fe7ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 英國倫敦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.9多國集會聲援<br />\n<br />\n另外，多個國家的海外港人發起6.9反送中集會，包括英國倫敦、加拿大多倫多、美國紐約、德國柏林、日本東京、澳洲悉尼等。<br />\n<br />\n■記者謝明明  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n陸委會：擬向港發旅警<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n憂變桂民海翻版 居德港人「剪護照」"},{"pid":"41c306cd120e9424e0190cc86d8c7213d67042b3","tid":1189749,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"noted."},{"pid":"9ae29a64a27a8c421d18bc06ef362f7f96ac5ad9","tid":1189749,"uid":87890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:59:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc610c1203db0d5f37d420755f4dcd387a44b9fc","tid":1189749,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}